OOC:I'll post for the trip, if you allow. I'll post just once for SS 
and he's back to you after, Kyle.

BIC: The ship's advance took some speed, and soon, it was heading for 
the Transwarp wormhole. Inside, Shadow Star deactivated 5 of the 6 
cannons and their power went directly into the shields.

Shadow Star: The cannons are all down except one, Sir. The shields are 
now at 200% of their normal capacity.

Tyrael: Perfect. Now, everybody hangs on to something.

The ship started to enter the transwarp passage. It shook heavily and 
started to revolve on itself.

Tyrael fell on the ground, but managed to transform to phoenix mode 
and to fly in the air. Shadow Star grabbed a bar and twisted it due to 
the speed of the ship.
